net.sf.mmm.util.reflect.base

Class GenericTypeBuilder<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.mmm.util.reflect.base.GenericTypeCapture<T>
      • net.sf.mmm.util.reflect.base.GenericTypeBuilder<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the generic type of the GenericType to build() after type variables have been bound.

    public abstract class GenericTypeBuilder<T>
extends GenericTypeCapture<T>
    This class allows to build instances of GenericType with custom binding for TypeVariables at runtime. The following example illustrates the usage: 
     public static GenericType<List<Provider<T>>> typeOfListOfProviderOf(GenericType<T> type) {
   return new GenericTypeBuilder<List<Provider<T>>>() {}
              .with(new GenericTypeVariable<T>() {}, type)
              .build();
 }
    Since:
    7.1.0
    Author:
    hohwille
